# Rubber Ball
# A highly elastic ball launched and allowed to bounce five times.
# Restitution 0.85 means it keeps 85% of its energy each landing.

simulate {
  gravity 9.8
  projectile ball {
    angle 50
    speed 35
    launch_from (0, 0, 0)
  }
  plot ball
  bounce ball times 5 restitution 0.85
  range ball
  max_height ball
}
